    "name": "Aestik",
    "steam_appid": 2199330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/0e69c4f0773e2cc1d194002d7cb989ec.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/0e69c4f0773e2cc1d194002d7cb989ec.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/0e69c4f0773e2cc1d194002d7cb989ec.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>手绘风格的银河战士恶魔城游戏，带有分支剧情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索艾斯蒂克之境时，你需要做出影响深远的决策，这将改变游戏的进程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个奇特而独特的世界中跳跃前行，揭示驱使理智生物陷入疯狂的神秘腐化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与野兽战斗，在严酷的环境中穿行，揭开世界互相连接的地图和隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索艾斯蒂克之境</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个庞大且互联的世界：</strong>穿越艾斯蒂克的复杂地图，发现隐藏的秘密，揭开这个世界的神秘面纱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的环境：</strong>艾斯蒂克的每个角落都有新发现，从温馨的泡泡森林到阴森的南瓜林地。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/3b6c0ef2f940bf91b92c4c9b17b70165.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/3b6c0ef2f940bf91b92c4c9b17b70165.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/3b6c0ef2f940bf91b92c4c9b17b70165.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战性障碍：</strong>用精准和技巧克服严峻的跳跃挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制你的游戏风格：</strong>装备符合你个人风格的能力符文，畅游世界！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/4574b0a2ceb5ab3c15c85a40671e57e6.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/4574b0a2ceb5ab3c15c85a40671e57e6.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/4574b0a2ceb5ab3c15c85a40671e57e6.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>对抗你的敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速战斗：</strong>与超过25种独特敌人进行快速战斗！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史诗级BOSS战：</strong>面对超过15个强大的BOSS，考验你的战斗技巧和策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/61534081067ca13edf9c1e32b376f01a.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/61534081067ca13edf9c1e32b376f01a.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/61534081067ca13edf9c1e32b376f01a.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>决定你的命运</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要选择：</strong>你的决定将改变冒险的进程，带来独特的遭遇！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重玩性：</strong>根据你选择的路径，体验不同的结局和故事线</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/8aa19028f306ac33a3bb45a16606a77b.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/8aa19028f306ac33a3bb45a16606a77b.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/8aa19028f306ac33a3bb45a16606a77b.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>额外功能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级路径：</strong>找到药水，选择不同的永久升级！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>图鉴：</strong>发现艾斯蒂克之境的所有生命形式，填满这本全面的指南！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘传送门：</strong>进入世界各地的传送门，完成挑战收集宝贵的碎片！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跟随者：</strong>找到可爱的小生物，带它们一起冒险！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>幽静的池塘：</strong>和布拉德莱一起休息，享受钓鱼的乐趣！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战模式：</strong>在主游戏之外接受各种挑战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>辅助选项：</strong>自定义设置，使游戏更加容易，帮助克服困难的部分，提升你的游戏体验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
